- But what you did was flat out vicious.

37:54.625 --> 37:57.041
- Just trying to get your attention.
- By humiliating me in public?

37:57.125 --> 38:00.041
Hey, you hurt me. If I have
to strike back hard to protect myself...

38:00.125 --> 38:02.583
Is that what you think this is? Combat?

38:02.667 --> 38:05.709
I've been taken for granted before and
I'm not going to let it happen again.

38:05.792 --> 38:08.875
If I'm going to give myself to you,
you damn well better worship me.

38:08.959 --> 38:12.250
And I will do that.
Morning and evening services.

38:12.709 --> 38:13.750
Good.

38:14.083 --> 38:15.542
But you have to stop treating
this relationship

38:15.625 --> 38:18.583
like it's a boxing match
only one of us can win.

38:18.667 --> 38:21.875
Maybe you haven't noticed,
but I'm in love with you.

38:21.959 --> 38:25.625
So it'd be nice if you could take
the gloves off and trust me.

38:26.709 --> 38:28.709
You're in love with me?

38:29.125 --> 38:30.458
Yeah.

38:33.333 --> 38:36.333
My campaign, that's about winning.

38:37.000 --> 38:40.500
This, you and me, it's about happiness.

38:42.875 --> 38:45.250
And we could both use a little.

38:48.083 --> 38:50.917
But maybe you need some more time
to think about it.

39:05.417 --> 39:08.041
Look, no gloves.

39:18.083 --> 39:22.000
Travers conked out the moment
his head hit the pillow.

39:22.083 --> 39:24.083
Poor little guy was beat.

39:24.417 --> 39:28.000
Well, he should be.
We covered every inch of that zoo.

39:28.333 --> 39:31.458
Oh, check this out.
You and Travers at the monkey house.

39:31.625 --> 39:34.125
Oh, I look squinty. Delete, delete.

39:35.750 --> 39:37.125
Oh, there's the one
the pretzel guy took.

39:37.208 --> 39:40.333
Oh, look at the three of us.
You have to e-mail me that one.

39:40.417 --> 39:41.500
Isn't that great?

39:42.542 --> 39:45.041
You know,
he thought that Travers had my eyes.

39:45.667 --> 39:48.250
- Seriously?
- He totally thought we were a family.

39:48.333 --> 39:53.417
Oh, well, if we were, we'd be one hell
of a good-looking one.

39:54.583 --> 39:57.333
Yeah. Nothing better than family.

40:26.917 --> 40:29.375
Oh, wow.

40:30.625 --> 40:32.959
And this time I really mean it.

40:33.041 --> 40:35.417
Yeah. Me, too.

40:40.834 --> 40:43.125
Well, you gonna say anything?

40:43.667 --> 40:46.583
To be honest,
I've heard better apologies.

40:46.875 --> 40:50.166
But I know how hard
this must have been for you,

40:50.250 --> 40:52.000
and that makes me happy.

40:52.083 --> 40:53.542
So I accept.

40:54.458 --> 40:56.792
Thanks. That's big of you.

40:57.291 --> 40:59.500
And it's big of you
to admit you're a chucklehead.

40:59.625 --> 41:00.667
I'll see you tomorrow.

41:03.083 --> 41:05.917
Did you hear that, Gilbert?
He apologised.

41:06.000 --> 41:09.583
I mean, I know he did it
just for her sake, but still.

41:11.333 --> 41:14.250
Maybe they have
a good marriage after all.

41:15.375 --> 41:19.250
But they'll never have what we had.
Will they, Gilbert?

41:20.291 --> 41:22.250
Not by a long shot.

41:25.000 --> 41:26.125
<i>Passion.</i>

41:26.208 --> 41:31.750
<i>It's a force so potent, we still</i>
<i>remember it long after it's faded away.</i>

41:33.709 --> 41:35.458
<i>A drive so alluring,</i>

41:35.542 --> 41:40.000
<i>it can push us into the arms</i>
<i>of unexpected lovers.</i>

41:42.208 --> 41:44.750
<i>A sensation so overwhelming,</i>

41:44.834 --> 41:49.875
<i>it can knock down walls we have built</i>
<i>to protect our hearts.</i>

41:50.917 --> 41:52.792
<i>A feeling so intense,</i>

41:52.875 --> 41:58.709
<i>it resurfaces even though</i>
<i>we tried so hard to keep it buried.</i>

42:00.750 --> 42:03.333
<i>Yes, of all emotions,</i>

42:03.417 --> 42:08.166
<i>passion is the one that gives us</i>
<i>a reason to live</i>

42:08.792 --> 42:14.417
<i>and an excuse to commit</i>
<i>all sorts of crimes.</i>
